parameters: It has a collar... It seems like someone's pet dog.
I wonder where this child's master went...

It's a terrible sight.... I can no longer believe that this
is the work of fellow humans....

To forcibly develop the land to this extent... What is
'Cordain' plotting...?
\SE[19]I guess we have no choice but to ask them directly.

\SE\SE[2]So you were here.... I found you. \SE[2]Huh... I'm
sure this is...

\SE[12]W-We forgot...!? \SE[99]When we came here, running
away with Vita who was being targeted by wolves...
\SE[100]You got angry and blew them away, right?

\SE[16]So that's what happened...! \SE[0]It feels like such
a long time ago, nostalgic...

\SE[2]Just in time. I was about to call out to you. \SE[3]I
was thinking of investigating this hole...
\SE[3]Huh...? Why do we need to investigate this hole?

\SE[74]I don't understand the reason for this hole.
\SE[3]It's probably part of Cordain's land development...
But there shouldn't be any notable resources around here.

\SE[2]Because there might be something we have overlooked...
\SE[3]It seems like we will form an investigation team to
thoroughly examine this hole.

\SE[19]You should tell them the truth...! \SE[31]If we keep
going like this, the soldiers of Ulyssean will start
meaningless digging holes...!

\SE[54]Th-That's troubling...! \SE[8]I need to confess and
ask for forgiveness quickly...!

\SE[16]Oh...! I heard it was terrible, but I didn't expect
it to be this bad...! \SE[15]It's almost like it could
become a tourist attraction...!

\SE[18]Honestly... It's an outrageous story, isn't it?
\SE[10]It's a desecration towards those who used to live
here.
\SE[13] (I-I missed the timing to speak up...)

\SE\SE[2]Well... it's true. \!\SE\SE[3]Even though it was an
emergency situation, it feels a bit wrong to trample on
animals that we don't even eat...\!\SE\SE[2]Morally, it
might have been bad. \!\SE\SE[3]...From my position, I can't
really say anything.

\SE[22]Cordain... Such despicable actions...! \SE[19]I want
to see the face of the person who dug such a huge hole...!

\SE[2]Huh...? \.This huge hole has nothing to do with
Cordain, right? \!\SE[3]And as for the face of the person
who dug it, we've already seen it, haven't we?
\SE[29]Um... I hope you won't get angry, but...

\SE[37]I-I got angry and... \SE[24]I... I did it... \SE[54]I
was being chased by so many wolves and... I got annoyed...!

\SE[74]Sigh... I was too tense for nothing... \!\SE[51]I
ended up making unnecessary calculations...
\SE[4]Oh, by the way, what happened to that dog...?

\SE[4]Ah, we ended up keeping it at our place. \SE[3]Its
name is Sable Noir.

\SE[4]Ah, Vega, are you afraid of animals by any chance...?
\SE[63]If that's the case, it would be troublesome...

\SE[76]I-I don't dislike them... \!\SE[18]It's just that I
haven't had much experience with them, so I'm not used to
it.

\SE\SE[0]Well then, it would be better to practice with
Sable Noir! \SE[0]I'm sure Sable Noir would also like to
play.

\SE[74]That's right... I wonder...? \SE[3]Is it okay? Like,
biting and stuff...?

\SE[17]It's okay...! \SE[15]Sable Noir is smart, you
know...! There's absolutely no way that would happen!

\SE[116]Ah...! So close, so close...!! \SE[43]I want to
gradually get used to it...!!

\SE[16]Even if you say that... the distance with dogs is
about that much...

\SE[43]Stop... Don't lick my face...! \!\SE[94]What's the
meaning of this...!?

\SE[69]Meaning...\.Is that so.... \!\SE[16]But, dogs are
that kind of creature...!

\SE[37]Ah...! \!\SE[86]I got bitten...!\.I got bitten a
little...!!

\SE[4]Ah... Sweet biting, huh. \SE[0]It's their way of
expressing affection. \SE[16]Dogs are just that kind of
creature, huh...!

\SE[108]Wow! You have quite sharp fangs...! \SE[43]I-Is it
okay to leave it like this after being bitten!?

\SE[14]Because originally I was a wolf...! \SE[15]So, I was
born with that kind of weapon! \SE[12]Though I'm not very
good at hunting with Sable Noir...!

\SE[13]Alright, I've become friends with Vega...!
\SE[12]When we return to the Ulyssean, we'll have to

using the bathroom...!

\SE[12]I'll play with you a lot...! \!\SE[18]You better be
prepared...!!
